        <definition>MLCoordinateFrameUID MLSpatialAnchor::cfuid</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>cfuid</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>The coordinate frame identifier of the Spatial Anchor. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This should be passed to MLSnapshotGetTransform to get the anchor&apos;s transform.</para>
<para>The anchor&apos;s transform is set when the anchor is created but may be updated later by the Spatial Anchor system based on factors such as quality of the mapped space and subsequent localizations. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
